{"id":718577329,"lang":"java","time":"5 days, 8 hours","timestamp":1654832061,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"8 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/718577329/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"45.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        HashMap<Character, Integer> hash = new HashMap<>();\n        int len =0;\n        int start =0;\n        for (int e =0; e<s.length();e++){\n            if(hash.containsKey(s.charAt(e))){\n                start = Math.max(start, hash.get(s.charAt(e))+1 );                \n                \n            }\n            hash.put(s.charAt(e),e);\n            len = Math.max(len, e-start+1);\n        }\n        return len;\n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
